msgctxt "title"
msgid "Garmin Index Smart Scale"
msgstr "Balance intelligente Garmin Index"

msgctxt "blurb"
msgid ""
"Let's be honest, tracking all those steps with a fitness wearable is nice. Seeing the benefits of all those steps when you take that step onto the scale is much nicer. Garmin's \"smart scale with "
"connected features\" gives you a way to bring all those metrics — weight, body mass index, body fat, skeletal muscle mass and more — together. Pair up this WiFi and Bluetooth connected scale with "
"the same app your Garmin fitness tracker uses and you've got all your fitness and body info right there in one place. Now get stepping."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "worst_case"
msgid ""
"Garmin seems to do a good job handling the privacy and security of all the personal data this smart scale collects. They did suffer that very public <a id=\"a1\">ransomware attack</a> in 2020. "
"Ransomware attacks suck and it seems no company is safe from them these days."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "worst_case"
msgid ""
"Garmin says they don’t sell your personal data to anyone. This is great. Garmin also seems to do a good job with what data they do share, which doesn’t seem to be too much. They ask for explicit "
"consent before sharing things like wellness data with third party wellness companies and emails for marketing."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "worst_case"
msgid ""
"Garmin may share or sell de-identified aggregate data collected by the Garmin Connect app with third parties to do things like make their features better or for research purposes. This doesn’t worry"
" us too much. Although now is a good time to remind you that it’s <a id=\"a1\">been found</a> to be pretty easy to de-anonymize some types of data and track down an individual’s patterns, especially"
" with location data. If you’re worried about this, you can opt out of using the Garmin Connect app to keep track of all the cool things it keeps track of. Which could be a bummer, but hey, also more"
" private."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "how_does_it_use_data_collected"
msgid ""
"Garmin clearly states they don't sell your personal information to anyone. They do say they may share or sell de-identified data collected by the Garmin Connect app: \"From time to time, we share or"
" sell activity data in a de-identified and aggregated manner with or to companies that provide Garmin and our customers with content or features for the purpose of enhancing the quality of the "
"content or features they provide and with or to other third parties for research or other purposes.\""
msgstr ""

msgctxt "how_does_it_use_data_collected"
msgid ""
"Some users wish to connect their Garmin accounts with their accounts on other platforms, such as Strava or MyFitnessPal, and they share a user’s data with such other platforms if directed to do so "
"by a user."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "how_does_it_use_data_collected"
msgid ""
"Garmin says they will only share most other forms of data like wellness data with wellness program provider, location data for navigation purposes or emails for marketing, with your explicit "
"consent."
msgstr ""
"Garmin assure partager la plupart des types de données autres que les données de bien-être avec les fournisseurs de programmes de bien-être, les données de localisation à des fins de navigation ou "
"les e-mails à des fins marketing, avec votre consentement explicite."

msgctxt "uses_encryption_helptext"
msgid "Garmin devices and apps use a combination of asymmetric and symmetric encryption appropriate to the nature and function of the product, and data stored/transmitted."
msgstr ""
"Les appareils et applications Garmin utilisent une combinaison de chiffrement asymétrique et symétrique adaptée à la nature et à la fonction du produit, ainsi qu’aux données stockées/transmises."

msgctxt "strong_password_helptext"
msgid "In order to use companion apps, an account with a strong password is required."
msgstr "Pour utiliser les applications compagnons, un compte avec un mot de passe fort est requis."

msgctxt "tips_to_protect_yourself"
msgid "Be very carefull who you chose to share your Garmin wellness data with."
msgstr "Faites très attention avec qui vous avez choisi de partager vos données bien-être Garmin."

msgctxt "tips_to_protect_yourself"
msgid "Adjust your <a id=\"a1\">privacy settings</a> in the Garmin Connect app to suit your comfort level."
msgstr "Ajustez vos <a id=\"a1\">paramètres de confidentialité</a> dans l’application Garmin Connect en fonction de votre niveau de confort."

msgctxt "tips_to_protect_yourself"
msgid "Don't connect your Garmin app to any social networks like Facebook."
msgstr "Ne connectez pas votre application Garmin à des réseaux sociaux comme Facebook."

msgctxt "personal_data_collected"
msgid "Name, email address, gender (optional), age (optional), date of birth (optional), photos (optional), location"
msgstr "Nom, adresse e-mail, genre (facultatif), âge (facultatif), date de naissance (facultatif), photos (facultatif), localisation"

msgctxt "biometric_data_collected"
msgid "Weight"
msgstr "Poids"

msgctxt "how_can_you_control_your_data"
msgid "Users can delete their data from their devices at any time."
msgstr "Les utilisateurs peuvent supprimer les données de leurs appareils à tout moment."

msgctxt "how_can_you_control_your_data"
msgid "Data provided to companion apps and servers is retained for as long as the user’s account is active. Users can delete their data from the companion apps and services at any time."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "track_record_details"
msgid "No known incidents in the last 3 years."
msgstr "Aucun incident connu au cours des 3 dernières années."

msgctxt "ai_helptext"
msgid "Garmin uses Machine Learning (ML) to provide personalized insights to customers who wish to receive them as they pursue their fitness and wellness goals."
msgstr ""
"Garmin utilise l’apprentissage automatique (Machine Learning, ML) pour fournir des informations personnalisées aux clients qui souhaitent les recevoir au fur et à mesure que les objectifs de fitness"
" et de bien-être sont atteints."

msgctxt "ai_what_can_it_do"
msgid "Garmin says in their privacy policy, \"Garmin does not make any decisions based on algorithms or other automated processing that significantly affect you.\""
msgstr ""
"Garmin déclare dans sa politique de confidentialité : « Garmin ne prend aucune décision basée sur des algorithmes ou d’autres traitements automatisés qui vous affectent de manière significative. »"
